      "text": [
        " - «لاَ بَأْسَ بِالصَّلاَةِ عَلَى اَلْبُورِيَاءِ وَ اَلْخَصَفَةِ وَ كُلِّ نَبَاتٍ إِلاَّ اَلثَّمَرَةَ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.804 - Muhammad ibn Muslim narrated from Imam Muhammad ibn Ali Al-Baqir (as) that He said:\n\"There is no issue with praying on mats made from reeds or on palm-leaf mats, and on any plant-based material, except for fruit”."
        ]
